{"comments":"SimplexNoise - improved gradient noise with better performance.\n\nKen Perlin's improved noise algorithm (2001), addressing the\ncomputational complexity and visual artifacts of classic Perlin noise.\n\n## Advantages over Perlin Noise\n\n- **O(n^2) vs O(2^n)**: Scales better to higher dimensions\n- **No axis-aligned artifacts**: Uses simplex grid instead of hypercube\n- **Better gradient distribution**: More isotropic appearance\n- **Lower computational cost**: Fewer multiplications per sample\n\n## Composition\n\nA molecule composed from Material pillar atoms:\n- NoiseFrequency: spatial frequency (0.0 to finite)\n- NoiseAmplitude: output range (0.0 to 1.0)\n- NoiseSeed: deterministic seed (any Int)\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\n-- Organic terrain noise\nterrain = simplexNoise\n  { frequency: noiseFrequency 0.5\n  , amplitude: noiseAmplitude 1.0\n  , seed: noiseSeed 12345\n  }\n\n-- High-frequency detail\ndetail = simplexNoiseDetail (noiseSeed 42)\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Surface.NoiseFrequency\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Surface.NoiseAmplitude\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Surface.NoiseSeed\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["frequency",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","NoiseFrequency"],"NoiseFrequency"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["amplitude",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","NoiseAmplitude"],"NoiseAmplitude"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["seed",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","NoiseSeed"],"NoiseSeed"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[100,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/SimplexNoise.purs","start":[96,22]},"title":"SimplexNoise"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","SimplexNoise"],"SimplexNoise"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[102,50],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/SimplexNoise.purs","start":[102,1]},"title":"eqSimplexNoise"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","SimplexNoise"],"SimplexNoise"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[109,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/SimplexNoise.purs","start":[104,1]},"title":"showSimplexNoise"}],"comments":"SimplexNoise - improved gradient noise configuration molecule.\n\nDescribes the parameters needed to generate Simplex noise.\nThis is pure data — actual noise generation happens at the runtime boundary.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[100,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/SimplexNoise.purs","start":[96,1]},"title":"SimplexNoise"},{"children":[],"comments":"Configuration record for creating SimplexNoise\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["frequency",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","NoiseFrequency"],"NoiseFrequency"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["amplitude",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","NoiseAmplitude"],"NoiseAmplitude"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["seed",{"annotat